page.title: 14MISS IRELAND'S GALA DAY
page.content: 6.00a.m. I got up to help decorate my house.Everything we used had something to do with{Ireland-a}thatched cottage,leprechauns,the Irish flag,a fishing net and flowers.10.00a.m. On to one of the floats to go for the Seton Queen 1985 and to the school for photos at 12.15. 12.45 p.m. In procession at the{War Memorial}for the wreath laying. 1.15 p.m. Embarked at { {COCKENZIE HARBOUR}for sailing to Port Seton Harbour. 2.30p.m. Presented to the Queen at the{CROWNING CEREMONY}in the park.Then at last we had tea. After all the excitement there was time to play with my friends before we had supper,watched a little television and wetn to bed.
